_sText:
Ok, so I noticed some bugs in my "final version" so I fixed them, and here it is. 
This map is just a multi-leveled map, and each floor is different. They are all unique, and one even has a secret heal area(on the + walkway) if you are willing to take the risk. I spent a lot of time on this, and it is probably my best real map.
Just enjoy, and have fun.
